  "response": "\"The night rolls on\" in the context of a song typically conveys the passage of time during the nighttime. It can evoke a sense of continuity, progression, or the unfolding of events as the night progresses. Depending on the context of the song, it might suggest a feeling of lingering moments, ongoing activities, or a mood that persists over the course of the night. This phrase can also imply a sense of endurance or the idea that time moves forward regardless of what happens.",
